        <p>Vitamin C is a required enzyme cofactor for collagen synthesis. Without adequate vitamin C, ingested collagen cannot be efficiently converted to new collagen in the body. The most evidence-supported pairing.</p>
        <span class="ac-btn">Read the Science &rarr;</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/beauty/biotin-gummies/" class="ac">
        <span class="ac-tag">Beauty Stack</span>
